ore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T06:11:38.000Z","msg":"好似無乜地方可以游水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有啲沙灘直頭仲封閉緊/係軍事禁區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T06:20:47.000Z","msg":"為咗防止共匪搶灘，對住廈門個邊嘅沿海，應該都插哂D叫軌條砦嘅柱係度，落唔到水，另外嘅地方我唔肯定有冇。<br />\n<br />\n不過去金門海邊，聽講去觀鳥嘅多，游水好似冇咩資料。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T07:44:58.000Z","msg":"唔該兩位巴打解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,冇水洗唔岩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cc90bd3f2b59acdfe81bbb559d5c669da7536e0","tid":770130,"uid":52623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T07:45:12.000Z","msg":"呢個係晌英國，荷蘭租私家車價錢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eabbbed1a6a87278141951029b979ca2a2972791","tid":770130,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4c47dfefed82585f612932a8730cd56b0b2ad04","tid":770130,"uid":52623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T07:44:15.000Z","msg":"八百台幣租一日電車，好貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T07:45:36.000Z","msg":"我都覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係咪包一舊電叉埋，即係叉電唔洗俾錢？"},{"pid":"00cbf8c12dc39d50ba9ac2195bf7b20f1310c4c1","tid":770130,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T07:47:24.000Z","msg":"800真係好貴<br />\n歐洲200港紙分分鐘租到一日棍波油私家車"},{"pid":"cf3cfabe29f8c9a48801f03f16a8b9a2fddc7e06","tid":770130,"uid":52623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T08:21:21.000Z","msg":"請問租普通單車、電油電單車幾錢？"},{"pid":"1f5f94eb61081dd2721bc929fd7708f8267b8312","tid":770130,"uid":61276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-07T08:21:54.000Z","msg":"之前係即場買"},{"pid":"b1a370f04dc100e990ceece47889f086552d80bd","tid":770130,"uid":52623,"like":0,"disl